Abuja-based socialite and businesswoman, Joke Sogunro, is bereaved. The usually happy Joke was deep in sorrow this week as she poured her grief unto the social media with the obituary poster of her late brother, Idris Nixon Sogunro. Stylish Joke Sogunro threw caution to the wind as tears rolled down her cheeks over the death of the one she calls ‘Aburo.’ Idris Nixon Sogunro was buried at Atan cemetery in Yaba early in the week. In Lagos, Joke Sogunro swayed into society limelight with her fashion business, Soggy’s Couture, on the Lagos mainland.